name: Cosmic Champs
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Cosmic Gold (COSG) is the governance token for Cosmic Champs which is a 3D, P2E, real-time strategy game on the Algorand blockchain. Travel around the cosmic universe to battle friends — or enemies — in real-time and earn tokens and NFTs. COSG is also used as a secondary P2E token and can be staked to earn rewards.
